.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_skill -  This returns just the skill level.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_skill(string skill)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^skill%^RESET%^ - the skill to return the level of
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the skill level

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/skills.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This returns just the skill level.  Used a lot to determine if you
can use/teach/whatever a skill.
This also uses a cache.
.EP

